staxel.village.dialogue.Wren.line:100002: (안함)Not many people talking to me on my rounds.
staxel.village.dialogue.Wren.line:100004: (안함)I have definitely been delivering everything correctly.
staxel.village.dialogue.Wren.line:100005: (안함)Hm? You want me to start collecting post from ^w:i;another^w:clear; ^c:1486b0;post office^c:pop;?
staxel.village.dialogue.Wren.line:100006: (안함)No thanks. I already have enough to do.
staxel.village.dialogue.Wren.line:100008: (안함)^c:1486b0;Robin^c:pop; is the one you want to talk to.
staxel.village.dialogue.Wren.line:100010: (안함)Really? You still won't leave me alone?
staxel.village.dialogue.Wren.line:100011: (안함)Alright. If it will get you to leave me alone, I'll go talk to the guy.
staxel.village.dialogue.Wren.line:100013: (안함)I already said I'd think about it.
staxel.village.dialogue.Wren.line:100014: (안함)You're not really going to get anything else out of me.
staxel.village.dialogue.Wren.line:100016: (안함)I don't have anything for you right now.
staxel.village.dialogue.Wren.line:100019: (안함)...can I get on with my rounds?
staxel.village.dialogue.Wren.line:100021: (안함)Is there something particular I can do for you?
staxel.village.dialogue.Wren.line:100023: (안함)There are worse places I could have been sent.
